headline: {'main': 'Apple Leads Way in Tracing Cobalt From Congo, Microsoft Lags-Amnesty', 'print_headline': 'Apple Leads Way in Tracing Cobalt From Congo, Microsoft Lags-Amnesty'}
snippet: Apple is leading the way in tracing cobalt used in its electronics to ensure the metal has not been mined by children in Democratic Republic of Congo while Microsoft is lagging, Amnesty International said.
